{"tid":474761,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"哥國大波女教師逼男生上床　唔做愛就搞到你「肥佬」","createTime":"2017-11-20T12:52:31.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-20T13:44:36.000Z","uid":20058,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"808db121e4d77dbb578077181153887deaacfd60","tid":474761,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T12:52:31.000Z","msg":"長輩及父母經常說，不好好學習考試會「零雞蛋」。哥倫比亞一名已婚中學女教師，就以協助學業為由，借故親近男學生；之後將自己的裸露影像傳給對方，又威脅若不與她做愛，就會直接把他們的成績「肥佬」。女教師的惡行近日曝光，丈夫憤而與她離婚，她亦面臨最高監禁40年的刑罰。 <br />\n<br />\n在去年1月至4月期間，40歲的約卡斯塔（Yokasta.M）利用職位之便，在校內物色多名年約16至17歲的「小鮮肉」男高中生。她先以教授功課為由接觸他們，取得聯絡方法後，透過WhatsApp傳送大量露乳照及色情短訊予男生；又威脅若不與她做愛，就會令他們不合格。多名男生屈服於其淫威之下，對她唯命是從。 <br />\n<br />\n直至近日，一名男生的父親在兒子手機內，發現多張約卡斯塔的裸照，逼問之下揭發淫師惡行，並報警求助。被捕的約卡斯塔除了教席不保，丈夫也與她離婚，更面臨40年徒刑。事件曝光後，有學生將相關影像放上網，有網民坦言：「這個我接受不到」、「學生的父親會報案，應該是出自同理心」。 <a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20171120/mobile/bknint-20171120180210857-1120_17011_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fint%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20171120%2Fmobile%2Fbknint-20171120180210857-1120_17011_001.html&d=MRqR8iGYkwLgGs7fsNJBmr%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=55a22461\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20171120/mobile/bknint-20171120180210857-1120_17011_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"fb79fea85fd4280597134d2e5a141bf2bba52754","tid":474761,"uid":4435,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T12:54:46.000Z","msg":"快"},{"pid":"6611b7d3ac2f1c60d2b87741656475554c07602e","tid":474761,"uid":4435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T12:55:11.000Z","msg":"當我冇講過"},{"pid":"30cf236feb6653d827c19fd3e505ae06765943da","tid":474761,"uid":36502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T12:55:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>快</blockquote><br />\n點"},{"pid":"75406fc59c393701ee8a1226d2f9327dc86ae19d","tid":474761,"uid":25837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T12:56:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>快</blockquote><br />\n點</blockquote><br />\n強"},{"pid":"d1f614ecc10e1ac8c8a799c86fdd8b37c9cd7f26","tid":474761,"uid":12269,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T13:15:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>快</blockquote><br />\n點</blockquote><br />\n強</blockquote><br />\n姦<br />\n你<br />\n三<br />\n個"},{"pid":"2ad227a9c9acdbd754bc17f421cbf1d22d4bf988","tid":474761,"uid":94828,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T13:17:55.000Z","msg":"好彩咩都冇講過"},{"pid":"8a2178081cee867a86a2646116d945c57e31d558","tid":474761,"uid":392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T13:32:31.000Z","msg":"40歲"},{"pid":"f0e5d71f90e31100ec6f35ddc5046de3113fdd47","tid":474761,"uid":19762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T13:39:42.000Z","msg":"中國依家有頭顱移植<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f3f425e79203bdb2dd74ea8fe98105718f7549f","tid":474761,"uid":137569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T13:43:10.000Z","msg":"快啲拉鳩佢"},{"pid":"5d65ecd64c58e0d1a7ad04fdf62d0c2dafaeeccc","tid":474761,"uid":100347,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T13:44:36.000Z","msg":"之前有人貼過啦<br />\n<br />\n快快快你老母咩 時事台特別多垃圾推呢啲post"}]}